    <section id="id1169615040518">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id1169611347331"><emphasis>Learning Outcome 1: </emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id1169617013026"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 1.10:</emphasis> We know this when the learner uses a range of techniques to perform written and mental calculations with whole numbers.</para>
    </section>
